{"tid":2104932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Poly醫療科學生實習","createTime":"2020-07-12T09:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T09:52:02.000Z","uid":28976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d836bf42c8eca821897e30a6f3e1c8979cb4256","tid":2104932,"uid":28976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T09:51:17.000Z","msg":"疫情一月第一次爆個陣ha同學校都好緊張，當晚就決定要停placement。Guideline明明話emergency level就唔比學生出，但其實我哋5月已經比人安排出翻實習<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。個陣冇乜個案就話唔驚姐，宜家日日三十單其實有d淆底，學生infection control又未必做得足，但ha同學校都完全冇消息話要停<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜update guideline都冇，醫院仲要唔比口罩我地用，d口罩係department拎錢買比我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。雖然我都好想快d出完畢業，但真心唔明點解爆得勁過第一波都唔suspend。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">票站要人</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d424f7edece7c59f6378111f14f034245cda1f","tid":2104932,"uid":28976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T09:52:02.000Z","msg":"入嚟話讀醫療科預咗個d同我死翻出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}